text:
When I went to Singapore, I went there with my friends.
Can women also enjoy it? I was a little worried, but it was a shop where even women could easily go and have fun without any worries.
I had a lot of fun with the attentive staff and cute girls who made me feel welcome.
We were able to sing karaoke in the private room, and it was a really fun night.
I would like to visit you again when I come to Singapore.
thank you very much.
